pairs, novel ligands that probe various properties of the steroid
pharmacophore, fluorescent neuroactive steroid analogues, and photoaffinity
labels. Using these tools, combined with receptor binding and electrophysiological
assays, we have begun to untangle the complexity of steroid actions
at this important class of ligand-gated ion channel.},
